Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:06.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:19.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:31.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:37.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:55.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:01:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:09.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:11.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:25.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:55.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Inoue completely fixed me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't seem like you'd die\Neven if you were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue healed Rukia as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking pretty long to recover…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot… Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her current injuries aren't the only\Nreason why she's been weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia didn't have enough time to\Nrecover her spiritual power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when the Bount mayhem occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and she was sent to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:30.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She needs time to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:32.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So are you finished cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Damaged buildings need\Nto be repaired
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the wounded need to be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is still damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:48.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like\Nwe're pretty much finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Seireitei has officially\Nacknowledged the Bounts’ existence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the reason for their creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:57.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:03.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, Kariya, wanted to\Nerase the Bounts' existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, he left a big impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you talk as if\Nyou know everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:15.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because\Nyou sent the Bounts here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You were with us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I defeated Gesell, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru is still damaged\Nbecause of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because you're weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so mad!\NI just let the truth slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just let what slip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:40.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky just because\Nyou got a little better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're just a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like a real Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away!\NGot it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your strange meekness is\Neven more unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Umm…\N– Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:17.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten\Nwhere you are, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If your business here is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,go back to the World of\Nthe Living immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got scolded because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did he come out after he was done\Neavesdropping on our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:50.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:59.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I can't get any sleep\Nwith you guys raising a ruckus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two don’t think of me\Nas an injured patient, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:24.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But man… I never thought that\NI would come to this world twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You meddle too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any Bounts left…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:42.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a battle that left\Nsuch unimaginable suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was too hung up about\Nthe Bounts' past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He probably couldn't stand\Nthings repeating themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:58.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… It's not easy living forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He saw the state of the Bounts\Nget worse countless times
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,over a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To him, history wasn't a line\Nthat stretched forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was something that revolved\Naround and around in a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to break that cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Revolving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:30.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're not transferring you\Nor anything extreme like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stationed\Nin the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:37.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You went there to support me\Nwhen you joined long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look, she doesn't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She erased it from her memory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because it was such\Na bad experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kuchiki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go bury yourself in the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm not some potted plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stationed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:03.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,within a four-kilometer radius\Naround Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With your skills, this mission\Nshouldn't be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.\NYou've got to get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… I'm feeling good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's only a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be anxious being\Nstationed by yourself for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. That sounds so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you informed Byakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No… Not yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… No…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:40.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki would probably\Ntell me not to inform him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,about every little thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I was going to leave\Nwithout informing him…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine if you think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go with peace of mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:02.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was the beginning\Nof everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until I met Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the future was\Na line that stretched on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I still believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:30.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby appoint Squad 11\NSixth Seat Renji Abarai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the position of Squad 6 lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:43.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I humbly accept this appointment,\NLieutenant Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.\NThat sounds so rigid…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway…aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:54.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten one step closer\Nto Byakuya Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ikkaku…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:01.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time\Nyou talk to Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's become an aristocrat,\Nyou're a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're more than equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You held out for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time you restore\Nyour relationship with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:19.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you used to run around\Nthe Rukon District together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki is supposed to be stationed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:28.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the World of the Living\Nfor a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Abarai, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:31.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be officially promoted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at the appointment ceremony\Na month from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When she comes back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surprise her by telling her that\NI'm a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If fate is a cog,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:56.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then all we can do is believe\Nthat whatever is turning it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is flawless,\Nas we move ahead…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the direction of\Nthe force of the fixed cogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:09.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…a blade is swung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so fell the sword of fate…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're…Yoshino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's not Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's Rantao…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is Rantao's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I carried you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:06.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so the Soul Reapers\Nwouldn't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:11.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with Ichigo Kurosaki\Nand the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kariya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:36.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Jokai Crest is backed\Nby all of the Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you withstand it,\NIchigo Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,People hate those\Nwho are superior to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends aren't any different!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I protect them because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd risk my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the fate of the Bounts\Nis to die out…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then I just have to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:27.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you should stay here\Nuntil your wounds heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rantao…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have anything to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on returning to Seireitei\Nafter all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to listen to the story\Nof the last Bount…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm returning to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've left the rest to Ukitake.\NThere's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:13:02.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Ichigo Kurosaki for me\Nfor stopping Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! No one's noticed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:21.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:28.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh. It's just you!\NDon't surprise me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:31.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard… You were trying to\Nsneak into Rukia's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me wanting\Nto be with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She and I are of one mind and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've devoted myself to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what in the world\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:46.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be sliced up by Byakuya's\NSenbonzakura if you go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:50.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you guys neglect me\Nway too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I finally\Ncaught up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,everything was over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:58.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I lost my chance\Nto play an active role!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An active role?\NYou wanted to be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think\NI came to this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right… I understand. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Senkaimon is just about ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:21.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's injured, so she has to\Nstay here to recover, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:25.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then I'm going to stay\Nby her side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in leaving you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only I were more powerful…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:40.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could pound the Bounts and\Nthe Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:45.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and make Sister adore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He gained that power and\Nwas swung around by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he had to destroy himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:03.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya wanted the power\Nto change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted was…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Revolving…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see?!\NDid you see this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the new Bad Shield Series!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:20.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bad… What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you enjoyed watching the DVD\Nof the TV version!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:27.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like this series!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I wasn't talking to you, Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like Stanley Ashford…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It doesn't just revolve.\N– …the guy who plays Ricky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It revolves…and whenever…\N– Julian, who plays Mille…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– the sun touches the moon…\N– is a much better actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– It seems that Mille dies in “2.”\N– Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:50.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…the world changes itself\Ninto something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…\NThen what's your favorite snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gotsubukko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Then you like\Nbaumkuchen as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:00.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Here's what your fortune says…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a perfect match…\Nfor me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're leading her on\Nwith those questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:11.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm going home soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have somewhere I need to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… Then see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there is something that\Ndoesn't change…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it would be my helplessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:35.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… So, boy, you really came…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry… She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can see spirits. I can touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That airplane…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:54.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was just something in my closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes they just disappear\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why\Nthey disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes they leave\Nbehind bloodstains
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that only I can see and\Nsomewhat painful feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:15.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I train my body,\NI can't protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:21.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I think about it,\Nmy heart feels like a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:34.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm late…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three dogs and six cats\Npassed me by today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… Did they say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The brown dog was really cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He kept peeing on the telephone pole,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many times\NI told him not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I brought you flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s revolving…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:21.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– If fate is a cog wheel…\N– I'll come back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:25.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– We are…\N– Thank you…mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,grains of sand crushed\Nbetween those cogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Don't cry anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– There is nothing we can do.\N– Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We just want power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s something we can’t easily protect,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we want to grab a sword beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:51.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power to crush fate surely\Nresembles a swinging blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is my strength the power\Nto crush fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or will I be consumed\Nby my power like Kariya was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in thinking about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This power is for protecting everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking about\Nwhy Kariya wanted to gain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya probably thought of history\Nas a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably trying\Nto sever it with force…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that's\Nright or wrong…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…even if things\Nrepeated themselves…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:44.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be that bad if\Nyou had friends there…right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that can\Nbe answered so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:20:00.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is history something that revolves\Nor stretches ahead of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's something that revolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,should we try to break that loop…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or be content with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, everyone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way\Nto this unknown world, Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:31.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is sad,\Nbut it's almost time to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're being mean again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go home, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Revolving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:30.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We tremble in awe of that\Nwhich cannot be seen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NSuch a cruddy little town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so fell\Nthe sword of fate once again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:54.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of a mask
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:19.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:23.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:32.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:41.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:43.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:51.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:53.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:23:00.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.76,0:23:02.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:04.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:12.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:14.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:17.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:23.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how've you all been! It's Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:32.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't appear much in Soul Society,\Nbut I'll play a big part
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when we get back to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. But with the new main character\Nof Bleach, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,appearing in the next episode,\Nyou don’t have any appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:39.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.59,0:23:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is… Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:52.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:55.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:57.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We just got back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.17,0:23:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are late, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we got lost in Kusajishi…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:02.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:04.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So where are the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:05.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo defeated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll fight Ichigo now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:11.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:13.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He already returned to\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:14.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard…\NWhen I see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him without even\Ngreeting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:22.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… You were right not to\Nsee him before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:27.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spy on others!